    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-08-30T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-08-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="117" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d117">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Denby</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 30,
                                1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Is ex-Viceroy Liu discharging duties in Szechuan or awaiting there
                            investigation commission? Should he be acting as viceroy pending <pb facs="0182" n="122" xml:id="pg_122"/> arrival successor, it is
                            proper, in view of the very serious charges against him, that he should
                            at once be relieved of all vice-regal functions. Can not ask punishment
                            until ascertainment offense.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
